                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Ripple of Fate"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Reflection</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/248396191/a0074558f99c36e32c2a642c89000de2_4486464436888383988.png",
                "id": "talent89438",
                "key": "Mirror Reflection of Doom",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Mirror Reflection of Doom"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Illusory Bubble</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Illusory Bubble</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When you deal Skill DMG</span>: Remove this status and double the DMG dealt for this instance.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/248396191/2e3cc81f7cf69d8fdf351f30e4e0993a_8304055387612298772.png",
                "id": "talent52491",
                "key": "Stellaris Phantasm",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Stellaris Phantasm"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive)<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> When you perform \"Switch Character\" while Mona is your active character</span>: This switch is considered a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fast Action</span> instead of a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Combat Action</span>. (Once per Round)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/248396191/a4683772d642e5af6323bd0a51d20fd7_1387419045473522218.png",
                "id": "talent96283",
                "key": "Illusory Torrent",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Illusory Torrent"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When your active character receives DMG</span>: Decrease DMG taken by 1.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span>. When the Usage is depleted, this card will not be discarded.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase</span>: Discard this card, deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1823644274202080312.png",
                "id": "talent22006",
                "key": "Reflection",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/1406b92c5115e3a534938a0d3638eeea_831591745626484824.png",
                "title": "Reflection"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_4320031315738829005.png",
                "id": "talent84340",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Fast Action</span></strong></p><p>You can continue with other actions after conducing 1 Fast Action. Only after conducting 1 Combat Action will the turn pass over to your opponent.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Combat Action</span></strong></p><p>After you finish 1 Combat Action, it will be your opponents turn.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Playing a card from your Hand with this rule is also a Combat Action rather than a Fast Action.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_857159913536521024.png",
                "id": "talent27529",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
